`` All the companies -LRB- NATO -RRB- hires , who owns the companies ? Americans , Chinese , Indians , Pakistanis . Why do n't you hire Afghans ? If you want to stop them from war , give them jobs . ...

`` My family , we have a lot of kids , no school . We need good schools , we need a system . ''

Hamid Ahang is a network engineer originally from Kabul .

`` There 's been certain progress , there are schools built . But at the same time , what they promised was stability and peace . After years of war , they have n't done as promised .

