Sima Quraishi is executive director of the Muslim Women Resource Center , a nonprofit based in Chicago . She is originally from Kabul .

`` There is a lot of money floating around -LRB- in Afghanistan -RRB- . However , I believe the money should be spent to help the people of Afghanistan with education/schools , job development , health care and child care .

